title: Lineage 2 Kamael Client +info for private server
description:

a txt file is up also to guide you through the install and *how to connect* to the server

- Do full installation Kamael Client.
- Run official autoupdater placed in your main L2 folder
- After you fully updated Delete Folder System
- Download our System mirror1
- Extract our System and paste to dir Lineage 2 folder
